This is a contextual lookup widget using the Wordnik API.

To install, drag this link to your bookmarks bar:

    <a href="javascript:(function(){var t=((new Date)*1);var s=document.createElement('script');s.type='text/javascript';s.src='http://localhost:3020/javascripts/wordnik_context.js?'+t;document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(s);})()">Wordnik Lookup</a>


